**Snippet:**

```java
EdgeCallback ec = (event,start,end) ->{
    if (event.getButton() == MouseButton.SECONDARY) {
        System.out.println(
                pg.rotateEdge(start,end) ?
                        "rotate edge successfully" :
                        "rotate edge  error"
        );
    }else if (event.getButton() == MouseButton.PRIMARY) {
        System.out.println(
                pg.deleteEdge(start,end) ?
